Text::Template::Simple
======================

A simple template class mainly for web applications.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

      Data::Dumper 2.101
      File::Spec   0.6
      File::Find   0
      IO::Handle   1.1505
      IO::File     1.06021
      Fcntl        1.03
      Safe         2.06

and this module is recommended:

      Devel::Size'  => 0,

All are available on CPAN.

